name: Tina Sprout | Black Bullet
description:
A lora based on the character Tina Sprout from Black Bullet


Use at 0.8~1.0 weights

  • No triggerwords for the look but adding "tinas" and "blonde hair" can help.

  • Use triggerword "tinasdress" to summon her in her classic green dress

  • Use triggerword "tinaspajamas" for the pajamas outfit

The pajamas outfit was trained with the "bare_shoulder" tag and is prone to gen NSFW.

Tested on :

  • Greymix

  • MidnightMelt

  • AOM3

  • Grapefruit

  • Kotosmix

  • Sweetmix

If you have any questions feel free to ask.
Kaïros#4463
Enjoy ♥
